## **Getting Started**

Start with the Canvas

The Canvas is the heart of Invook. It’s where your files, notes, conversations, and AI assets come together in one visible space. Instead of switching between tools and tabs, you work directly on the Canvas while everything stays connected.

What is Invook?

Invook is a unified AI workspace where assets are generated, organized, and shared without losing context. AI creation typically happens across disconnected tools, drives, chats, and exports. Invook brings generation, storage, and collaboration into one system.

Why Canvas-first matters?

AI work often becomes fragmented across tools. This leads to re-uploading assets, losing prompts and iterations, broken context between ideas and files, and friction when sharing with collaborators or clients. Invook treats AI assets as first-class files, ensuring your thinking stays where you left it.
